    {
      "type": "fillblank",
      "text": "What ______ you doing?",
      "answer": "are"
    },
    {
      "type": "fillblank",
      "text": "I ______ reading a book.",
      "answer": "am"
    },
    {
      "type": "translate",
      "cn": "他正在做什么？",
      "en": [
        "What is he doing?"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "funFacts": [
    "现在进行时（present continuous tense）用来描述正在进行的动作，通常由\"be动词 + 动词-ing\"构成。",
    "在英语中，我们用\"What are you doing?\"来询问别人正在做什么，这是日常对话中很常用的表达。"
  ]
